{"tid":1198951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想趁呢個時候提下勇敢既朋友同埋出過黎既人","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:32:11.000Z","uid":165699,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35049c5419ef174caa4108893804799d30655e45","tid":1198951,"uid":165699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"而家唔係時候屌大啦 我知大家好嬲啲人早走<br />\n但係唔走都走左 而家屌黎咩用？？<br />\n香港重要啲定你條氣重要啲？<br />\n快啲提下身邊中間或者溫和既大爭取下佢地支持仲好 佢地都可以好有作為架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經叫左幾個fd買左啲野我幫手送過去<br />\n<br />\n重申一次唔衝有唔衝時作用 衝既都有佢地既作用 大局為重啊啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n<br />\n我尋日都早走 我都對唔住你地 所以我要做翻啲野 無野做既人 唔該 同我買啲野去支援義士<br />\n蹦帶 膠布 生理鹽水 m巾（你無睇錯）雨傘 眼罩 手套 保鮮紙 大聲公<br />\n食物 食水！仲有其他whatever 出到既帶野 出唔到既叫人幫你<br />\n<br />\n係咁多 11/12見"},{"pid":"462c5be359511742d9ae293ea5c82b34f759b636","tid":1198951,"uid":165699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b30141ad8ff11863b12981c4c7592986df31049","tid":1198951,"uid":165699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4732158bcc5875f9e021cccc18f684358589c2e9","tid":1198951,"uid":165699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"我明白有人有包袱 其他人都唔好屌人住"},{"pid":"7e024d072ed11eda1ba2b7ce5782578f3653a7d9","tid":1198951,"uid":144529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"人會到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3772b94f59f6fc849ee1063d4fa4ace9c11f3eb8","tid":1198951,"uid":165699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e024d072ed11eda1ba2b7ce5782578f3653a7d9","tid":1198951,"uid":144529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"人會到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:1